{"type":"text","timestamp":1775879666930,"sessionID":"ses_2855485c2ffeiU9p9SZjJiSl0T","part":{"id":"prt_d7aacfe27001gVzEfWqFrneFjr","messageID":"msg_d7aace8230017593q0HevrjFyR","sessionID":"ses_2855485c2ffeiU9p9SZjJiSl0T","type":"text","text":"## Verification Report: AR-030 — Helm Chart 模板与 Values\n\n### Overall Status: ⚠️ PARTIALLY COMPLIANT\n\n**Summary:** Most requirements are implemented, but several critical gaps exist.\n\n---\n\n### ✅ PASSING Requirements\n\n| Requirement | Status | Evidence |\n|------------|--------|----------|\n| **REQ-030.1: Chart.yaml Metadata** | ✅ | `apiVersion: v1`, `name: agentcube`, `version: 0.1.0`, `appVersion: 1.0.0` present |\n| **REQ-030.2: values.yaml Configuration** | ✅ | All configuration sections present (redis, router, workloadmanager, volcano) |\n| **REQ-030.3: WorkloadManager Deployment** | ✅ | Deployment + Service with env, probes, resources working |\n| **REQ-030.4: Router Deployment** | ✅ | Deployment + Service with WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL, probes |\n| **REQ-030.5: WorkloadManager RBAC** | ✅ | ServiceAccount, ClusterRole, ClusterRoleBinding complete |\n| **REQ-030.6: Router RBAC (Optional)** | ✅ | Conditional rendering works when `router.rbac.create: true` |\n| **REQ-030.7: Volcano Scheduler (Optional)** | ✅ | Conditional rendering works when `volcano.scheduler.enabled: true` |\n| **REQ-030.9: CRD Files** | ✅ | Both `agentruntimes` and `codeinterpreters` CRDs present |\n| **REQ-030.11: Helm Lint** | ✅ | `helm lint` passes with 0 failures |\n| **REQ-030.11: Helm Template** | ✅ | Generates valid YAML (validated with Python yaml parser) |\n\n---\n\n### ❌ FAILED Requirements\n\n| Requirement | Status | Issue |\n|------------|--------|-------|\n| **REQ-030.1: Chart.yaml Keywords** | ❌ | Missing `keywords` field |\n| **REQ-030.1: Chart.yaml Maintainers** | ❌ | Missing `maintainers` field |\n| **REQ-030.1: Chart.yaml Home/Sources** | ❌ | Missing `home` and `sources` fields |\n| **REQ-030.2: Router resources** | ❌ | Missing `router.resources.requests` in values.yaml |\n| **REQ-030.3: WorkloadManager probes** | ⚠️ | Port should use named port `http` instead of numeric port |\n| **REQ-030.4: Router probes** | ⚠️ | Port should use named port `http` instead of numeric port |\n| **REQ-030.8: Redis Secret Template** | ❌ | **Missing file** `templates/redis-secret.yaml` |\n| **REQ-030.10: .helmignore** | ❌ | **Missing file** `.helmignore` |\n| **REQ-030.7: Volcano Scheduler args** | ⚠️ | Uses `--kubeconfig=/etc/kubernetes/kubeconfig` instead of `--config=/config/agent-scheduler.conf` |\n| **REQ-030.7: Volcano Scheduler volumes** | ⚠️ | Volume names differ from spec (`config-volume` vs `config`) |\n\n---\n\n### 📋 Missing Files\n\n1. **`manifests/charts/base/.helmignore`** - Required for chart packaging\n2. **`manifests/charts/base/templates/redis-secret.yaml`** - Required for Redis password Secret\n\n---\n\n### 🔍 Test Files Status\n\n- ✅ `tests/workloadmanager_test.yaml` - Present\n- ✅ `tests/agentcube-router_test.yaml` - Present\n- ✅ `tests/workloadmanager-rbac_test.yaml` - Present\n- ✅ `tests/rbac-router_test.yaml` - Present\n- ✅ `tests/volcano-scheduler_test.yaml` - Present\n\n**Note:** Tests cannot run without `helm-unittest` plugin installed.\n\n---\n\n### Critical Issues to Fix\n\n1. **Add missing `.helmignore` file**\n2. **Add missing `templates/redis-secret.yaml` template**\n3. **Add Chart.yaml metadata** (keywords, maintainers, home, sources)\n4. **Fix Volcano Scheduler deployment** to match spec (config volume mount, args)","time":{"start":1775879666928,"end":1775879666928}}}
